sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User as EndUser
    participant API as AIRequestService
    participant PS as PromptSecurityService
    participant DB as SecurityPatternDB
    participant PG as LlamaPromptGuard2
    participant CI as ContentInspector
    participant Presidio as MicrosoftPresidio
    participant OPA as OPA
    participant Guard as OutputGuard
    participant LLM as AIModels_LLM

    User->>API: POST prompt (JWT)
    API->>PS: scan_messages()
    PS->>DB: load active regex patterns
    DB-->>PS: weighted jailbreak rules
    PS->>PS: regex score (pattern weights)
    PS->>PG: classify injection (threshold 0.85)
    PG-->>PS: injection confidence
    alt cumulative score >= block threshold
        PS-->>API: ScanResult blocked
        API-->>User: 403 injection blocked
    else allowed
        PS-->>API: ScanResult allow
        API->>CI: inspect_content()
        CI->>Presidio: detect PII in prompt
        Presidio-->>CI: entities found
        CI-->>API: sensitivity escalated if PII
        API->>OPA: evaluate policy
        OPA-->>API: allow
        API->>LLM: stream generation
        loop each token
            LLM-->>API: token chunk
            API->>Guard: redact PII (Presidio)
            Guard-->>User: SSE safe token
        end
    end
